00:29:04,430 --> 00:29:07,400
“并深信我们所从事的...”
"and believed strongly in what we were doing..."

175
00:29:07,600 --> 00:29:10,570
“我们参与了大战中 最重要的军事行动”
"We were involved in one of the most important operations of the war."

176
00:29:10,770 --> 00:29:13,260
“艾尔使我们能团结一致”
"Al was the one who held us all together."

177
00:29:13,470 --> 00:29:15,060
“他身先士卒”
"He was the first to volunteer."

178
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:18,300
“那里有四千人的部队开过”
"We passed a road where over 4,000 troops had passed."

179
00:29:18,510 --> 00:29:23,500
“尊夫尽忠职守...”
"Your husband served in a unit whose duty is to place itself beyond..."

180
00:29:23,710 --> 00:29:26,580
“大家都很怀念他”
"...which we all cherish and hold dear..."

181
00:29:26,780 --> 00:29:30,380
“李等人的死 对军团打击甚大”
"The loss of Lee and others like him is a distinct blow to the regiment."

182
00:29:30,590 --> 00:29:33,490
“我们了解你想知道...”
"We understand your desire to learn about"-

183
00:29:33,690 --> 00:29:36,680
“他去世时的情形”
"the circumstances leading to his death."

184
00:30:28,910 --> 00:30:31,880
上校  有件事想告诉你
Colonel, I've got something you should know about.

185
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:36,980
这两人在诺曼第阵亡
These two men died in Normandy.

186
00:30:37,190 --> 00:30:41,280
这位死于奥哈马海滩 肖恩瑞恩
-This one at Omaha Beach.  -"Sean Ryan."

187
00:30:42,390 --> 00:30:46,490
这位死于犹他 彼得瑞恩
-This man at Utah.  -"Peter Ryan."

188
00:30:50,670 --> 00:30:53,460
这位上周在新几内亚阵亡
This man was killed last week in New Guinea.

189
00:30:56,540 --> 00:30:58,970
丹尼尔瑞恩
"Daniel Ryan."

190
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:01,580
他们是兄弟
The three men're brothers,sir.

191
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:06,840
他们的妈妈会在下午 接到这三封电报
I just learned that this afternoon their mother's going to get all three telegrams.

192
00:31:09,950 --> 00:31:14,220
在抢滩前一晚 他们的四弟跟随101空降师
There's also a fourth brother who parachuted in with 101st Airborne -

193
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:17,720
在诺曼第某处跳伞
the night before the invasion. He is somewhere in Normandy.

194
00:31:17,930 --> 00:31:20,290
他还活着吗? 不知道
-Is he alive?   -We don't know.

195
00:31:24,230 --> 00:31:26,130
跟我来
Come with me.

196
00:33:09,910 --> 00:33:12,640
该死
Goddammit.

197
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:16,300
四兄弟都在第29师的 同一个连队服役
All four were in the same company in the 29th Division -

198
00:33:16,510 --> 00:33:19,170
但苏利文兄弟在朱诺送命后 我们便分开了他们
but we split them up after the Sullivan brothers died on the Juneau.

199
00:33:19,380 --> 00:33:22,550
能联络上四弟詹姆斯吗?
Any contact with the fourth son, James?

200
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:28,090
不能  他空降在距纽维15哩的 内陆  深入了敌区
No. He was dropped 15 miles inland near Neuville, behind German lines.

201
00:33:28,290 --> 00:33:33,350
根本无法知道他空降在哪里
Mac, there is no way you can know where he was dropped.

202
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:37,500
据报101空降师的人失散了
First report from lke's people at SHAEF said the 101st is scattered.

203
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:39,830
诺曼第有很多 被空投错误的部队
There are misdrops all over Normandy.

204
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:44,300
就算瑞恩能安然降落 也无法找到他
Assuming Private Ryan even survived the jump, he could be anywhere.

205
00:33:44,510 --> 00:33:46,600
可能他早已阵亡
In fact, he's probably K.I.A.

206
00:33:46,810 --> 00:33:50,300
老实说  若我们派出搜救部队
And frankly, if we go sending some sort of rescue mission, -

207
00:33:50,510 --> 00:33:54,350
他们就得穿越德军固守区
flat-hatting throughout German reinforcements along our advance, -

208
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:57,450
那一定也会阵亡的
they're going to be K.I.A., too.

209
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:21,140
这里有封信
I have a letter here...

210
00:34:23,010 --> 00:34:29,040
是很久以前给波士顿的 比克斯比太太的信  听我读
...written a long time ago to a Mrs Bixby in Boston. So bear with me.

211
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:33,050
“女士”
"Dear Madam."

212
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:38,380
“我已从麻萨诸塞州 上将副官的...”
"I have been shown in the files of the War Department a statement" -

213
00:34:38,590 --> 00:34:40,360
“战争部档案得悉”
"of the Adjutant General of Massachusetts" -

214
00:34:40,550 --> 00:34:44,120
“你是五位在沙场上”
'that you are the mother of five..."

215
00:34:46,570 --> 00:34:50,590
“光荣阵亡的战士的母亲”
"...sons who have died gloriously on the field of battle."

216
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:57,670
“我感到我的言辞薄弱无力”
"I feel how weak and fruitless must be any words of mine" -

217
00:34:57,880 --> 00:35:01,370
“根本无法安抚你的悲伤”
'that would attempt to beguile you from the grief' -

218
00:35:01,580 --> 00:35:04,850
“也无法弥补你的损失”
"of a loss so overwhelming..."

219
00:35:05,050 --> 00:35:10,740
“但我必须要在此向你致谢”
"...but I can't refrain from tendering the consolation that may be found" -

220
00:35:10,950 --> 00:35:15,620
“他们是为了拯救国家而死”
"in the thanks of the republic they died to save."

221
00:35:19,390 --> 00:35:23,860
“愿天主安抚你的丧子之痛”
"May our Heavenly Father assuage the anguish of your bereavement" -

222
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:29,260
“让你永远怀念远去的挚爱”
"and leave you only the cherished memory of the loved and lost" -

223
00:35:29,470 --> 00:35:33,180
“神圣的荣耀都归于你们”
"and the solemn pride that must be yours to have laid such a sacrifice" -

224
00:35:33,380 --> 00:35:39,000
“因你们为自由 付出了重大的代价”
"upon the altar of freedom. Yours very sincerely and respectfully," -

225
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:41,420
“林肯敬上”
"Abraham Lincoln."

226
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:06,430
那孩子还活着 我们要派人去找他
That boy is alive. We are going to send somebody to find him.

227
00:36:06,640 --> 00:36:10,630
然后带他远离战场
And we are going to get him the hell out of there.

228
00:36:13,790 --> 00:36:17,950
奥哈马海滩 登陆后第三天

229
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:27,350
后勤官在海滩 寻找被炸毁的碉堡
The Quartermaster's up the beach a way. Look for a blown-up bunker.

230
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:30,800
我是C连的米勒 上尉  请进
-Miller,Charlie Company.  -Go on in,Captain.

231
00:36:31,010 --> 00:36:34,000
若六点以前无法下坦克的话
If we don't off-load the Shermans by 0600 -

232
00:36:34,210 --> 00:36:39,070
一整师的部队 就会被困在卡伦坦
we'll have a division stuck at Carentan with its pants around its ankles.

233
00:36:39,270 --> 00:36:41,550
再说明一下
Well, you let me know of it.

234
00:36:41,750 --> 00:36:45,010
让C连死守维尔维里 直到装甲兵开到
Let Charlie Company hold at Vierville 'til we can get the armour there.

235
00:36:45,210 --> 00:36:46,840
传令兵
Runner!

236
00:36:52,930 --> 00:36:56,550
原本空降师该打开缺口的 但他们却投错地方
Airborne was supposed to win an open door for us, but misdropped, -

237
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:59,600
全都失散了  你的情况如何?
and scattered all their sticks into the wind. What's your situation?

238
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:02,850
第四区攻下了
Yes, sir... Sector Four is secure.

239
00:37:03,060 --> 00:37:10,000
我们摧毁了这几处的 88公厘炮
We took out towed 88s here, here and here.

240
00:37:10,210 --> 00:37:12,970
敌军有四部坦克和一些运兵车
They got four Shermans and some deuce-and-a-halves.

241
00:37:13,170 --> 00:37:16,110
这两处的布雷区很大
These two minefields are actually one big one.

242
00:37:16,310 --> 00:37:20,190
我们到了中心地带 发现地雷的密度很高
We went up the middle of it, but it turned into a mixed high-density field.

243
00:37:20,390 --> 00:37:23,470
什么地雷都有  S44型、S42型
A little bit of everything; Sprengmine 44s, Schumne 42s, -

244
00:37:23,680 --> 00:37:29,020
散片型地雷、A-200 连侦测器都无法找到
pot mines, A-200s, the little wooden bastard the detectors don't pick up.

245
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:34,750
这里埋了T43型大地雷 大概想炸我们的坦克
Here, they placed big mushrooms, Teller mine 43s, I guess for our tanks, -

246
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:38,240
从这里到村庄的边缘
from here right up to the edge of the village, right here.

247
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:40,470
已记下位置  通知了工兵
We marked them and called the engineers.

248
00:37:40,680 --> 00:37:44,160
有遇上反抗吗? 没想像的那么强
-Resistance?  -We had higher support expectations.

249
00:37:44,370 --> 00:37:48,710
有一连没配大炮的346步兵
There was a company without artillery. Wehrmacht. 346th Infantry.

250
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:52,040
由卡夫加帕指挥 我们俘虏了23人
Von Lucke Kampfgruppe. We ended up with 23 prisoners.

251
00:37:52,240 --> 00:37:54,710
已交由29师的宪兵处置
We turned them over to MPs from the 29th.

252
00:37:58,030 --> 00:38:00,750
我军的伤亡呢?
What about our casualties?

253
00:38:00,950 --> 00:38:07,980
伤亡人数是...35死  70人伤
Well, the figure is... We're 35 dead, times two wounded.

254
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:12,150
他们就是不肯放弃那些重炮
They just didn't want to give up those 88s.

255
00:38:13,270 --> 00:38:15,960
任务很艰巨  所以才找你
It was a tough assignment. That was why you got it.

256
00:38:16,170 --> 00:38:18,540
是  长官
Yes, sir.

257
00:38:18,750 --> 00:38:20,670
约翰
John...

258
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,890
你又有一项任务了 是  长官
-I've got another one for you.   -Yes, sir.

259
00:38:26,090 --> 00:38:28,250
是上级直接交办的
It's straight from the top.

260
00:38:33,420 --> 00:38:38,860
我希望你和我带一队人 到纽维去执行公关任务
I wish. You and I are taking a squad to Neuville on a PR mission.

261
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:41,120
由你带队吗?
Oh, are you leading a squad?

262
00:38:41,330 --> 00:38:45,590
一位二等兵死了三兄弟 所以能回家
A private in the 101st lost three brothers and he's got a ticket home.

263
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,960
为何要去纽维呢? 他们觉得他在那里
-Why Neuville?  -They think he's there.

264
00:38:48,170 --> 00:38:51,070
他是被错投的空降部队之一
Part of all those Airborne misdrops.

265
00:38:51,270 --> 00:38:55,370
现在兵荒马乱 要找一名士兵很难
It won't be easy finding one soldier in the middle of this goddam war.

266
00:38:55,570 --> 00:38:57,600
就像大海捞针般
Like finding a needle in a stack of needles.

267
00:38:57,810 --> 00:38:59,300
那连上兄弟怎么办?
What about the company?

268
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:02,640
最好的跟我们 其他的加入B连
We take the pick of the litter, the rest goes to Baker.

269
00:39:02,850 --> 00:39:06,910
天啊  他们夺走了你的连?
Jesus Christ! They took away your company?

270
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:11,220
部队是军方的  我们唯有遵命
It wasn't mine, it was the Army's. So they told me, anyway.

271
00:39:11,420 --> 00:39:15,220
给我莱宾、杰克森、韦德 贝斯里和卡帕佐
Get me Reiben on BAR, Jackson, Wade, Beasley and Caparzo.

272
00:39:15,430 --> 00:39:18,450
贝斯里死了 那找梅利西
-Beasley's dead.  -Alright,Mellish then.

273
00:39:18,660 --> 00:39:21,500
有人会法语吗? 据我所知没有
-Do have a guy who speaks French?    -Not that I know of.

274
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:25,930
塔尔博特呢? 今早死了
What about Talbot? This morning.

275
00:39:26,140 --> 00:39:29,200
我要去找个翻译员
I'm going to try and dig up another interpreter.

276
00:39:29,410 --> 00:39:32,430
到滩头的车辆调度场集合
Assemble at the battalion motor pool on the beach.

277
00:39:32,640 --> 00:39:35,080
该怎么办? 听着  什么?
What are we going to do? Listen up. What?

278
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:39,050
我要用大块乳酪塞进你的屁股 好让你棺材盖国旗回家
Go home wrapped in the American flag with a hunk of cheese in your ass.

279
00:39:39,250 --> 00:39:42,450
我以为你喜欢塞屁股的 什么?
I thought you liked it in the ass. What?

280
00:39:42,650 --> 00:39:45,050
立正
Attention!

281
00:39:45,260 --> 00:39:47,850
稍息  我要找提摩西厄本下士
As you were. I'm looking for Corporal Timothy Upham.

282
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:50,050
是  我就是厄本
Yes, I'm Upham.

283
00:39:50,260 --> 00:39:52,420
你会说法语和德语? 是  长官
-Do you speak French and German?    -Yes, sir.

284
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:54,620
有没有口音? 法语有
-How's your accent?   -Slight one in French.

285
00:39:54,830 --> 00:39:56,930
但德语很纯正 很好
-My German's clean.    -Very good.

286
00:39:57,140 --> 00:40:00,830
你已被派给我了 收拾行囊  我们要到纽维去
You've been re-assigned to me. Grab your gear, we're going to Neuville.

287
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:04,480
这是何时更新的? 早上八点半
-When was this updated?    -As of 8:30 this morning.

288
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:07,870
这是12SS坦克部队 还有两队人向南推进
This is the 12th SS Panzer. These are the two axes advancing south.

289
00:40:08,080 --> 00:40:13,070
纽维有德军 我知道  下士
There are Germans in Neuville. I understand, Corporal.

290
00:40:13,290 --> 00:40:16,950
纽维有很多德军 有问题吗?
There are a lot of Germans in Neuville. You've got a problem with that?

291
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:20,650
我没作战过 只懂绘制地图和翻译
Please consider that I've never been in combat. I make maps and translate.

292
00:40:20,860 --> 00:40:24,060
我需要会法语和德语的人
I need someone who speaks French and German.

293
00:40:24,260 --> 00:40:28,360
原来的两位阵亡了 我从新兵训练后就没拿过枪
My two guys were killed. I haven't held a weapon since training.

294
00:40:28,570 --> 00:40:31,000
基本训练时开过枪吧?
Did you fire the weapon in Basic training?

295
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:34,640
开过  长官 那去准备一下
-Yes, sir.   -Well, then get your gear.

296
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:38,210
长官  我能带...
Sir, may I bring...

297
00:40:42,410 --> 00:40:44,640
能带打字机吗?
May I bring my typewriter, sir?

298
00:40:50,090 --> 00:40:51,850
是  长官
Yes, sir.

299
00:40:54,560 --> 00:40:56,320
谢谢你
Thank you very much.

300
00:40:56,530 --> 00:40:58,620
那是纪念品吗? 不是
-Is that a souvenir?    -No, sir.

301
00:40:58,830 --> 00:41:00,590
慢慢来
Take your time.

302
00:41:05,370 --> 00:41:07,930
下士  凡事都有好的一面
You should look on the bright side of things, Corporal.

303
00:41:08,140 --> 00:41:12,300
是 还有  这个也没有用
-Yes. -For one thing, you don't need those.

304
00:41:12,510 --> 00:41:16,570
但你需要这个 对  要这个
-You'll need that.   -Yes. I'll need this, not that.

305
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:15,000
你好 干嘛?
Hey! Hey!

306
00:42:15,210 --> 00:42:17,440
你是不是想找死?
You want your head blown off?

307
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:22,510
别再用你的爪子碰我 回去你的岗位
Don't touch me with those rat claws again. Get the fuck back in formation!

308
00:42:24,120 --> 00:42:26,520
我只是想问你来自哪里
I was just wondering where you're from.

309
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:35,120
卡帕佐  对吧? 滚开  下士
-Caparzo,is it?  -Drop dead,Corporal.

310
00:42:35,330 --> 00:42:36,520
知道了
Gotcha.

311
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:40,360
每次你向上尉敬礼 就会惹来德军袭击他
Every time you salute the Captain,you make him a target for the Germans.

312
00:42:40,570 --> 00:42:42,470
对不起 帮帮忙  别那么做
-I'm sorry.  -Do us a favour.Don't do it.

313
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:45,300
尤其是 当我站在他旁边时  懂吗?
Especially when I'm standing next to him.Capisci?

314
00:42:45,500 --> 00:42:48,600
懂了 下士  那是什么书?
-Capisco.  -Corporal,what's your book about?

315
00:42:48,810 --> 00:42:50,100
当心你的枪 对不起
Watch your rifle. Sorry.

316
00:42:50,310 --> 00:42:55,250
是关于行军时 发展手足之情的方法
It's about the brotherhood that develops between soldiers during war.

317
00:42:55,450 --> 00:42:59,080
手足之情? 你懂什么是手足之情?
Brotherhood? What do you know about brotherhood?

318
00:42:59,280 --> 00:43:01,310
要注意这砘
Get a load of this guy, Fish.

319
00:43:01,520 --> 00:43:04,080
你何不去问上尉是哪里人呢?
Why don't you ask the Captain where he's from?

320
00:43:04,290 --> 00:43:07,690
去问他  他什么都会告诉你的
Ask the Captain. He'll tell you everything you want to know about him.

321
00:43:09,230 --> 00:43:11,130
解释给我听
Explain the maths of this to me.

322
00:43:11,330 --> 00:43:15,270
八个人为何要 冒险救一个人呢?
Where is the sense in risking the lives of the eight of us to save one guy?

323
00:43:15,470 --> 00:43:18,400
20度  有人想回答吗?
20 degrees. Anybody wants to answer that?

324
00:43:18,600 --> 00:43:21,700
莱宾  想想那可怜虫的妈妈吧
Reiben, think about the poor bastard's mother.

325
00:43:21,910 --> 00:43:24,030
医护兵  我也有妈妈
Hey, Doc, I've got a mother.

326
00:43:24,240 --> 00:43:26,570
你有妈妈  中士也有妈妈
You've got a mother, Sarge has got a mother.

327
00:43:26,780 --> 00:43:30,270
我敢说上尉也有妈妈
Shit, I bet even the Captain's got a mother.

328
00:43:30,480 --> 00:43:33,250
也许上尉没有  但我们全都有
Maybe not the Captain, but the rest of us.

329
00:43:33,450 --> 00:43:35,750
“不问原因  只求为国牺牲”
"Their's is not to reason why their's is but to do and die"

330
00:43:35,950 --> 00:43:40,250
下士  那是什么鬼意思?
What the fuck is that supposed to mean, Corporal?

331
00:43:40,460 --> 00:43:41,790
我们都该死吗?
We're all supposed to die?

332
00:43:41,990 --> 00:43:45,660
厄本说的是我们的职责 是  长官
-Upham's talking about our duty.  -Yes, sir.

333
00:43:45,860 --> 00:43:46,890
我们全都得服从命令
We all have orders to follow.

334
00:43:50,300 --> 00:43:54,200
是的  长官  谢谢 就算任务是“苦差”?
Yes, sir. Thank you. Even if the mission is "FUBAR"?

335
00:43:54,410 --> 00:43:56,900
这才更加要服从
Especially if the mission is "FUBAR".

336
00:43:57,580 --> 00:44:01,310
“苦差”是什么? 是德语
-What's "FUBAR"?  -It's German.

337
00:44:01,510 --> 00:44:03,640
没听过
Never heard of that...

338
00:44:03,850 --> 00:44:07,980
长官  我对此有点意见
Sir, I have an opinion on this matter.

339
00:44:08,190 --> 00:44:10,880
说出来听听吧
By all means, share it with the squad.

340
00:44:11,090 --> 00:44:13,320
我的想法是
From my way of thinking, -

341
00:44:13,530 --> 00:44:18,290
这次任务 浪费了宝贵的军事资源
this mission is a misallocation of valuable military resources.

342
00:44:18,500 --> 00:44:20,330
是吗?继续
Yeah? Go on.

343
00:44:20,530 --> 00:44:26,130
我觉得上帝赐给我打仗的天分
It seems to me that God gave me a sepcial gift made me a fine instrument of warfare.

344
00:44:26,340 --> 00:44:30,170
莱宾  听好  这样抱怨才对 继续  杰克森
Reiben,pay attention.Now, this is the way to gripe.Continue,Jackson.

345
00:44:30,380 --> 00:44:35,810
要是他派我这个狙击手
If He was to put me and this sniper rifle anywhere up to and including -

346
00:44:36,010 --> 00:44:39,210
到希特勒一哩范围内
one mile of Adolf Hitler with a clear line of sight, sir...

347
00:44:39,420 --> 00:44:42,650
大家就能收拾行囊回家 战争就结束了  阿们
Pack your bags, fellas, the war is over. Amen.

348
00:44:42,850 --> 00:44:45,080
乡巴佬  这主意不错
That's brilliant, bumpkin.

349
00:44:45,290 --> 00:44:48,120
上尉  你呢?你不会抱怨吗?
What about you, Captain? You don't gripe at all?

350
00:44:48,330 --> 00:44:51,590
我是上尉  身负重任 不会向你抱怨
I don't gripe to you. I'm a captain. There's a chain of command.

351
00:44:51,800 --> 00:44:53,590
上级永远是发牢骚的对象
Gripe always go up.

352
00:44:53,800 --> 00:44:58,600
你向我发牢骚 我向我上级发牢骚  如此类推
You gripe to me, I gripe to my superior officers, and so on.

353
00:44:58,800 --> 00:45:02,670
我不会在你面前发牢骚 你是突击队员  应该明白
I don't gripe in front of you. You should know that as a Ranger.

354
00:45:02,870 --> 00:45:07,540
对不起  就当你不是上尉 或我是少校吧
I'm sorry, but let's say that you weren't a captain or that I was a major.

355
00:45:07,750 --> 00:45:09,480
你会说什么?
What would you say?

356
00:45:09,680 --> 00:45:13,580
那样我就会说 这项任务棒极了
In that case, I'd say, "This is an excellent mission" -

357
00:45:13,790 --> 00:45:18,220
意义重大  值得我全力以赴
"with a valuable objective worthy of my best efforts."

358
00:45:18,420 --> 00:45:23,990
而且我对瑞恩的母亲 感到深切的悲痛
"Moreover, I feel heartfelt sorrow for the mother of Private Ryan" -

359
00:45:24,200 --> 00:45:29,460
为了慰藉她 我愿意赔上我与部下的性命
"and I'll lay down my life and those of my men, especially yours, Reiben," -

360
00:45:29,670 --> 00:45:31,160
尤其是你  莱宾
'to ease her suffering."

361
00:45:32,540 --> 00:45:34,900
他很棒 我喜欢他
He's good. I love him.

362
00:45:45,350 --> 00:45:47,150
算了
Fine!

363
00:46:28,390 --> 00:46:31,520
打雷! 闪电!
-Thunder!  -Flash!

364
00:46:31,730 --> 00:46:35,530
厄本  到那边去 莱宾  你们四个过去
Upham, over there. Reiben, you four go.

365
00:46:44,440 --> 00:46:46,310
去吧!
Go, go, go, go!

366
00:46:51,880 --> 00:46:54,820
很高兴看见你 希尔中士  救星来了
You are a sight for sore eyes. Sergeant Hill, our reliefs showed up.

367
00:46:55,020 --> 00:46:59,120
有多少人? 八个  但不是救兵
-How many are you?   -Eight. We're not your relief.

368
00:46:59,320 --> 00:47:02,590
为什么? 我们来找二等兵瑞恩
What do you mean, sir? We're here for a Private Ryan.

369
00:47:02,790 --> 00:47:05,230
谁? 瑞恩?为什么?
Who? Ryan? What for?

370
00:47:05,500 --> 00:47:08,730
他在这里吗? 大概在镇的另一边
-Is he here?  -Maybe on the other side of the town.

371
00:47:08,930 --> 00:47:11,430
周围都有德军  很难通过
It's hard to get to. The Germans punched a hole in our centre.

372
00:47:11,640 --> 00:47:14,570
我军给德军切断 他叫什么名字?
-They cut us right in two.  -What's his name,again?

373
00:47:14,770 --> 00:47:17,870
瑞恩  詹姆斯瑞恩 隶属101空降师
Ryan, James Ryan. He dropped in with the 101st.

374
00:47:18,080 --> 00:47:21,100
高德曼  找传令兵来 传令兵
Goldman, get me a runner! Runner!

375
00:47:21,310 --> 00:47:23,210
来吧
Come on!

376
00:47:26,920 --> 00:47:29,320
琼斯  让开
Jonesy, make a hole up there!

377
00:47:30,990 --> 00:47:33,920
我们为东面的炮火所阻
We got stopped by fire from the eastward.

378
00:47:34,130 --> 00:47:37,750
德军聚集了两个团的兵力
The Germans have been reinforcing two regiments all day.

379
00:47:37,960 --> 00:47:40,020
已经有四十五分钟没有动静
It's been quiet for 45 minutes.

380
00:47:40,230 --> 00:47:42,670
德军正把火力集中于西面
The Germans concentrate their fire westward.

381
00:47:42,870 --> 00:47:46,170
谁在广播? 达伍德迪撒多夫
Who's that on the loudspeaker? Dagwood Duesseldorf.

382
00:47:46,370 --> 00:47:50,870
友善的政战官
Our friendly neighbourhood morale officer.

383
00:47:51,080 --> 00:47:54,340
“自由神像完蛋了”
"The Statue of Liberty is kaput."

384
00:47:54,550 --> 00:47:56,910
想扰乱我们军心
That's disconcerting.

385
00:48:01,390 --> 00:48:05,620
笨蛋  你爹的包皮已给割掉了
Your father was circumcised by my rabbi, you prick!

386
00:48:08,960 --> 00:48:10,480
躲好
Cover!

387
00:48:17,400 --> 00:48:19,100
去吧
Go!

388
00:48:42,230 --> 00:48:44,960
去你的臭混蛋 伏下
You sadistic fucking animals! Get down.

389
00:48:45,160 --> 00:48:48,030
敌人知道我军通讯中断 所以针对传令兵
They know we're not in direct contact. They'll single out the runners.

390
00:48:48,230 --> 00:48:49,790
为什么要射杀他们?
Why do they shoot them up?

391
00:48:50,000 --> 00:48:53,560
不能留活口  以防军情外泄 我们也会这样做
As long as his lungs are working, he carries the message. We'd do the same.

392
00:48:53,770 --> 00:48:57,300
不  我们不会 韦德  准备起程
No, we wouldn't! Wade! Get them ready to travel.

393
00:48:57,510 --> 00:48:59,340
博伊德 来吧
Boyd! Come on!

394
00:48:59,540 --> 00:49:02,210
再试一遍  设法通知 汉米尔上尉  我们正赶过去
Try again! Let Captain Hamill know we're coming.

395
00:49:02,410 --> 00:49:04,680
纽维其他地方怎么样?
What's the rest of Neuville like?

396
00:49:04,880 --> 00:49:08,680
接着会看到两层建筑物 有很多窗户
The next block's got two-storey buildings. A lot of windows.

397
00:49:08,890 --> 00:49:10,950
有一广场可作藏身之用
There's a square with good cover.

398
00:49:11,160 --> 00:49:13,560
带我去  中士  留在这里
Show me. Sarge, hold right here!

399
00:49:13,760 --> 00:49:15,190
遵命
Yes, sir!

400
00:49:19,430 --> 00:49:21,990
别在这里挨打  到里面躲避
Stay out of this enfilade and use the buildings.

401
00:49:22,200 --> 00:49:25,140
到左边去  边走边开火 我们各派两人
Try a left hook. Shoot and scoot. Two of yours, two of mine.

402
00:49:25,340 --> 00:49:27,830
黑斯亭斯、高德曼  到前面去
Hastings, Goldman! Up front!

403
00:49:28,970 --> 00:49:31,640
莱宾、卡帕佐 通讯仍受敌军干扰
Reiben, Caparzo. They're still jamming us.

404
00:49:31,840 --> 00:49:34,900
尽快到角落去  小心行事
Short runs, high and low at the corners. It's going to be tight.

405
00:49:35,110 --> 00:49:37,480
准备进行近身战  去吧
Be prepared for close contact. Go.

406
00:49:37,680 --> 00:49:40,150
厄本  跟霍瓦特中士待在一起
Upham! You stay with Sergeant Horvath.

407
00:49:40,350 --> 00:49:44,380
上尉  我会像内裤般粘着他
Stay here! I'll wear him like underwear, Captain. You stay with me.

408
00:49:53,030 --> 00:49:55,470
广场闸口在大楼的尽头
Past the end of the block are the gates of the square.

409
00:49:55,670 --> 00:49:57,640
好 好的
Good. Alright.

410
00:50:05,010 --> 00:50:06,740
莱宾  上尉从哪里来的?
Reiben, where's the Captain from?

411
00:50:06,950 --> 00:50:10,680
猜中的话有奖 奖金三百块
If you figure it out, you'll get a prize. 300 bucks, last I heard.

412
00:50:10,880 --> 00:50:14,370
大家下注  最少五块
The company's got a pool. Five bucks gets you in.

413
00:50:21,430 --> 00:50:24,950
就在拐弯处  躲到闸门后面去
It's around this corner. Defilade right up to those gates.

414
00:50:26,500 --> 00:50:28,800
一定有人知道他来自何方
Somebody must know where he's from.

415
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:31,970
我跟他一起那么久也毫无头绪
I've been with him since Casserene Pass. I don't have a clue.

416
00:50:32,170 --> 00:50:37,010
我的足踝很痛 战事没结束已经要坐轮椅
My ankles are killing me. I'll need a wheelchair before the war is over.

417
00:50:37,210 --> 00:50:41,470
老天  就跟老妇一样
That's it! Oh, my God! That ankle is like an old woman.

418
00:50:41,680 --> 00:50:45,050
就像...老天
Like an old... Oh, God!

419
00:50:46,350 --> 00:50:49,580
莱宾?你连他上哪所学校 也不知道?
Reiben. So you don't even know where he went to school?

420
00:50:49,790 --> 00:50:54,020
他没念书 是军部用大兵尸体组装而成
He didn't go to school. They assembled him at OCS out of dead Gls.

421
00:50:54,230 --> 00:50:57,560
我知道他的来历
Pay attention to detail. I know where he's from and what he did -

422
00:50:57,760 --> 00:50:59,860
因为我看得仔细
because I pay attention to detail.

423
00:51:00,070 --> 00:51:03,330
厄本  别信他的鬼话
Hey, Upham! Careful you don't step in the bullshit.

424
00:51:08,870 --> 00:51:11,140
去吧 打雷
Do it. Thunder!

425
00:51:11,340 --> 00:51:13,870
打雷  不然开火
Thunder, or we will fire on you!

426
00:51:14,080 --> 00:51:17,070
梅利西、卡帕佐  过来
Mellish, Caparzo, come here!

427
00:51:23,890 --> 00:51:26,720
叫他们表明身分
Tell them to show themselves.

428
00:51:38,600 --> 00:51:41,300
问问德军在哪里
Ask them where the Germans are.

429
00:51:45,840 --> 00:51:48,010
他说什么? 孩子
What is he saying? Something about the children.

430
00:51:48,210 --> 00:51:50,370
孩子? 他想我们带走孩子
Kids? He wants us to take them.

431
00:51:50,580 --> 00:51:52,310
不行  不能带走孩子
No, no. We can't take the kids.

432
00:51:52,520 --> 00:51:58,010
不可以  不行
We can't take the kids! No, no!

433
00:52:00,230 --> 00:52:03,190
他们以为这样较安全 跟着我们不会安全
They think they'll be safe. They won't be safe with us!

434
00:52:04,700 --> 00:52:07,160
你疯了?听从上尉的命令
Are you nuts? Listen to the Captain!

435
00:52:07,770 --> 00:52:09,670
他们以为孩子会安全一点
They think they'll be safe with us.

436
00:52:09,870 --> 00:52:15,310
什么地方也不会安全 卡帕佐  交回孩子
It's not safe anywhere. Caparzo! Put that kid back!

437
00:52:17,080 --> 00:52:20,010
卡帕佐  把孩子还给他们 请放心
Caparzo, put the girl back! It's OK, it's OK.

438
00:52:20,210 --> 00:52:22,370
交回孩子
Give that kid back!

439
00:52:23,550 --> 00:52:27,280
厄本  怎么说请放心? 他让我想起外甥女
Upham, how do you say, "It's OK?" I can't. She reminds me of my niece.

440
00:52:27,490 --> 00:52:29,420
把孩子交回去
Get the kid back up there!

441
00:52:29,620 --> 00:52:33,020
最少也该把她带到下个市镇
We should at least take her to the next town.

442
00:52:33,260 --> 00:52:36,320
我们有任务在身 不是来救孩子
We're not here to do that, we're here to follow orders!

443
00:52:36,530 --> 00:52:39,660
中士  把孩子接过来
Sarge, take this goddam kid!

444
00:52:39,860 --> 00:52:42,530
躲好
Cover, cover!

445
00:52:50,040 --> 00:52:51,240
糟糕
No!

446
00:52:51,440 --> 00:52:53,340
可恶  哪里射过来的?
Goddammit! Where did that come from?

447
00:52:56,010 --> 00:52:59,110
听到枪声前他已倒地
He was on the ground before we heard the shot.

448
00:53:04,390 --> 00:53:06,360
是我就会到那里
That's where I'd be.

449
00:53:08,060 --> 00:53:12,090
我看不到 450码外  也许在阴暗处
I didn't see it. 450 yards, maybe a shade under.

450
00:53:12,300 --> 00:53:16,060
大家别冒险出去 那枪手很厉害
I wouldn't venture out there, fellas. This sniper's got talent!

451
00:53:20,710 --> 00:53:25,610
别哭  我带你找爸妈
Please don't cry. I'll take you back to Mama and Papa. Please don't cry.

452
00:53:25,810 --> 00:53:27,110
来吧
Come on.

453
00:53:29,810 --> 00:53:31,010
卡帕佐
Carpy!

454
00:53:42,460 --> 00:53:45,400
上尉 撑着  卡帕佐
Captain! Hold on, Caparzo.

455
00:53:46,360 --> 00:53:48,330
扶我起来  我走得动
Help me up. I can walk.

456
00:53:48,530 --> 00:53:50,160
卡帕佐  别动
Caparzo, stay still!

457
00:54:02,050 --> 00:54:04,910
两格  风向偏左
Two clicks. Left wind.

458
00:54:08,120 --> 00:54:09,950
笨蛋
Fish!

459
00:54:17,300 --> 00:54:19,860
上尉?看到他吗?他怎么了?
Captain, can you see him? How is he?

460
00:54:20,060 --> 00:54:22,160
韦德  别乱来
Wade, you stay put.

461
00:54:22,370 --> 00:54:24,530
上尉  他哪里中枪?
Where is he shot, Captain?

462
00:54:26,270 --> 00:54:28,600
看得到他吗? 别出去
Can you see him? You stay there!

463
00:54:28,810 --> 00:54:31,170
可恶  躺下来
Damn it! Stay down!

464
00:54:31,380 --> 00:54:36,010
你怎么了?你中了枪 要我照顾吗?
What's the matter with you? Am I going to take care of you if you get hit?

465
00:54:36,210 --> 00:54:38,050
笨蛋  过来
Fish, come over here!

466
00:54:38,250 --> 00:54:41,840
卡帕佐  躺下来别动
Carpy, put your head down! Why can't you put your head down?

467
00:54:50,400 --> 00:54:53,560
天主  我信靠你
Oh, my God, I trust in Thee.

468
00:54:53,770 --> 00:54:59,570
别让我蒙羞  别让敌人战胜我
Let me not be ashamed. Let not my enemies triumph over me.

469
00:55:08,780 --> 00:55:13,050
抄下来  替我寄出去
Copy it. Copy it and send it for me.

470
00:55:13,250 --> 00:55:15,810
放下来  你自己寄
You're going to send it yourself. Put it down!

471
00:55:16,020 --> 00:55:17,990
信沾了血 我知道
-It's got blood on it!   -I see it.

472
00:55:22,790 --> 00:55:27,490
给我爸的  沾了血  笨蛋
It's... It's to my dad. It's got blood on it, Fish.

473
00:55:55,930 --> 00:55:58,260
打中了  伏下
We got him. Stay down.

474
00:56:07,140 --> 00:56:10,540
伤得很重? 胸口中弹  或许肺给打中了
How bad is it? Chest, maybe lung shot.

475
00:56:26,820 --> 00:56:29,220
把大炮放到街上
Get that.30 up the street!

476
00:56:34,030 --> 00:56:36,560
报告情况 上面安全
Detail! Clear, up!

477
00:56:36,770 --> 00:56:38,330
下面安全
Clear, down!

478
00:56:53,250 --> 00:56:55,810
老早说过不能带孩子
That's why we can't take children.

479
00:57:02,190 --> 00:57:05,630
霍瓦特中士  检查武器
Sergeant Horvath, do an ammo check.

480
00:57:05,860 --> 00:57:09,320
厄本  把水壶装满
Upham, canteens. Fill them up.

481
00:57:10,130 --> 00:57:11,830
希尔中士 是的  长官
-Sergeant Hill.   -Yes, sir.

482
00:57:12,040 --> 00:57:16,230
召集弟兄  在广场西北角集合
Gather your men. We'll form up at the northwest corner of the square.

483
00:57:16,440 --> 00:57:18,000
杰克森 是
-Jackson.   -Sir!

484
00:57:18,210 --> 00:57:23,340
梅利西  去检查那座塔 尽快回来  快去吧
Mellish. Check the tower, hustle back here. Right now, go!

485
00:57:34,690 --> 00:57:36,590
去他的瑞恩
Fuck Ryan!

486
00:57:46,940 --> 00:57:51,140
打雷 闪电  进来吧
Thunder! Flash! Come on in!

487
00:57:55,780 --> 00:57:58,010
我们在找汉米尔上尉
Hey, guys. We're looking for Captain Hamill.

488
00:57:58,220 --> 00:58:01,010
那边  过了广场就到 过了广场
Down there, across the square. Across the square.

489
00:58:01,220 --> 00:58:03,380
提防狙击手
Go easy. Watch for snipers.

490
00:58:04,820 --> 00:58:06,590
请坐
Sit down.

491
00:58:22,240 --> 00:58:25,400
吉米  叫汉米尔上尉过来
Jimmy T. Go and find Captain Hamill. Bring him here.

492
00:58:25,610 --> 00:58:29,570
什么?上面吗? 我怎么知道?自己去找
-What? Up there?   -How should I know? Go and look!

493
00:58:29,780 --> 00:58:31,540
谢谢你  智障
Thank you, you moron.

494
00:58:33,220 --> 00:58:38,310
先在这里休息一下
Alright. You guys just flake out here for a while.

495
00:58:39,990 --> 00:58:43,590
我要把石子倒出来
Let me get this goddam hitchhiker out of my boot.

496
00:58:53,800 --> 00:58:57,570
放下武器 立刻放下
Put your weapons down! Drop them now!

497
00:59:01,650 --> 00:59:03,440
我会开枪的
I'll shoot you!

498
00:59:03,650 --> 00:59:05,050
放下武器
Drop, drop 'em!

499
00:59:08,220 --> 00:59:09,950
立刻放下武器
Put 'em down!

500
00:59:25,570 --> 00:59:27,160
上面安全了
Clear, up!

501
00:59:32,380 --> 00:59:34,740
可恶
Shit, shit!

502
00:59:34,950 --> 00:59:37,240
上面安全了
Clear, up!

503
00:59:37,450 --> 00:59:39,380
下面也安全了
Clear, down!

504
00:59:51,330 --> 00:59:52,760
这样子够让人变老了
Enough to make you old.

505
00:59:54,130 --> 00:59:55,330
但愿如此
Let's hope so.

506
01:00:05,480 --> 01:00:09,280
101师前导部队的汉米尔 第二突击队的米勒
Hamill, Pathfinders 101st. Miller, 2nd Rangers.

507
01:00:09,470 --> 01:00:12,010
谢谢
Thank you.

508
01:00:12,220 --> 01:00:14,680
我们在找二等兵瑞恩 他是你的属下
We're looking for a Private Ryan. He's part of your outfit.

509
01:00:14,890 --> 01:00:16,910
有可能找到他吗?
Any chance that you policed him up?

510
01:00:17,520 --> 01:00:22,460
路上的情况如何? 风光明媚  弹药快用光了
How was the road in? Scenic. We lost most of our ammo.

511
01:00:22,660 --> 01:00:24,630
还死了一位队员
Not to mention one of our men.

512
01:00:24,830 --> 01:00:29,100
中尉 把火箭筒调换到右边的路旁
Lieutenant! Redeploy that bazooka to the right side of the road.

513
01:00:29,300 --> 01:00:31,530
去带瑞恩过来
And get Ryan up here!

514
01:00:33,440 --> 01:00:38,260
瑞恩...到前面来
Ryan! Ryan! Front and centre! Ryan!

515
01:00:41,980 --> 01:00:44,210
我们的大爷来了
Here comes our boy.

516
01:00:51,460 --> 01:00:53,480
我早说他是个混蛋
I told you he was an asshole.

517
01:00:55,560 --> 01:00:58,220
二等兵瑞恩报到 稍息
Private Ryan reporting as ordered. At ease.

518
01:00:58,430 --> 01:01:02,200
第二突击队的米勒上尉 有话跟你说
Captain Miller, 2nd Rangers, wants a word with you.

519
01:01:03,470 --> 01:01:05,630
这边
This way.

520
01:01:05,840 --> 01:01:09,070
蹲下吧
Alright. Take a knee.

521
01:01:18,110 --> 01:01:20,450
二等兵  有个坏消息要告诉你
Private, I'm afraid I have some bad news for you.

522
01:01:29,250 --> 01:01:33,320
这真是让人难以启齿...
Well, there isn't any really easy way to say this, so...

523
01:01:35,220 --> 01:01:38,600
我就直说吧  你的兄弟死了
...so I'll just say it. Your brothers are dead.

524
01:01:39,900 --> 01:01:44,520
我们奉命来找你
We have orders to come and get you...

525
01:01:44,730 --> 01:01:46,760
你可以回家了
...because you're going home.

526
01:02:00,890 --> 01:02:02,980
老天  我兄弟死了
Oh, my God! My brothers are dead!

527
01:02:10,970 --> 01:02:14,770
我本想带他们去钓鱼的
I was going to take them fishing when we got home.

528
01:02:28,350 --> 01:02:32,540
对不起  詹姆斯 真是不知该说什么
I'm so sorry, James. I can't tell you how much.

529
01:02:32,750 --> 01:02:38,160
他们是怎样死的? 阵亡
-How did they die?   -They were killed in action.

530
01:02:40,230 --> 01:02:42,350
没有可能
That can't be.

531
01:02:44,230 --> 01:02:47,630
他们才在念中学
They can't be my brothers. They're still in grammar school.

532
01:02:50,670 --> 01:02:54,030
你是詹姆斯瑞恩? 对
-You're James Ryan?   -Yeah.

533
01:02:54,750 --> 01:02:57,340
爱阿华州的 詹姆斯法兰西斯瑞恩?
James Francis Ryan from lowa?

534
01:02:57,550 --> 01:03:00,940
明尼苏达州的 詹姆斯腓德利克瑞恩
James Frederick Ryan, Minnesota.

535
01:03:07,420 --> 01:03:11,440
那表示我弟弟没事吗? 对  我确信他们很好
-Does that mean my brothers are OK?   -Yeah,I'm sure they're fine.

536
01:03:11,650 --> 01:03:14,590
你确定? 我们找的不是这个瑞恩
Are you sure? We're looking for a different Ryan.

537
01:03:14,790 --> 01:03:16,230
只是误会而已
It's just a big foul-up.

538
01:03:17,130 --> 01:03:20,860
你怎么能确定? 怎么知道是不是又弄错了
How can you be sure? How do you know that the foul-up isn't -

539
01:03:21,060 --> 01:03:23,050
原来是他的弟弟没事
that his brothers are OK, and...

540
01:03:23,260 --> 01:03:25,320
中尉 麻烦你了
Lieutenant. I'm sorry for the trouble.

541
01:03:25,530 --> 01:03:30,700
我在离开前才刚给他们写信 我得回家去了
I just wrote them a letter before I left. I've got to get home.

542
01:03:30,910 --> 01:03:35,720
我要立刻回家  我想回家
I've got to get home right now. I want to go home.

543
01:03:36,390 --> 01:03:37,750
我们的瑞恩在哪里呢? 不知道
Where is our Ryan? Don't know.

544
01:03:37,960 --> 01:03:41,970
可以跟指挥官联络一下吗? 瑞恩隶属于什么单位?
Are you in touch with your CO? What unit's Ryan in?

545
01:03:42,180 --> 01:03:46,150
506团的B连 那个断脚的砘锸506团的
Baker Company, 506th. The guy with the broken foot's in 506th.

546
01:03:46,360 --> 01:03:48,820
我想是C连吧 你想?
-Charlie, I think.   -You think?

547
01:03:49,020 --> 01:03:52,790
瑞恩?我不知道...老天
Ryan? Don't know... Man!

548
01:03:52,990 --> 01:03:55,470
你们在哪里降落? 维尔维里
-Where was your dropzone?    -Vierville.

549
01:03:55,670 --> 01:03:58,390
维尔维里?那怎会到这来的?
Vierville? How did you end up here?

550
01:03:58,600 --> 01:04:01,690
问倒我了 C-47受到猛烈的攻击
You got me, sir. The C-47 took heavy fire.

551
01:04:01,900 --> 01:04:04,390
机师拼命闪避炮火
Pilot went crazy turning every which way.

552
01:04:04,610 --> 01:04:08,740
跳伞时炮火更猛 情况混乱  我就来了这里
We took more fire in the drop. It got messy. I ended up here.

553
01:04:08,940 --> 01:04:12,040
我没见过我的队友 天晓得他们在哪里
I haven't seen a single guy from my stick. God knows where they are.

554
01:04:12,250 --> 01:04:15,880
有B连的人谈到空降区在哪吗
Did anybody from Baker Company talk about where the dropzone was?

555
01:04:16,080 --> 01:04:19,380
没有  但大家的集合点一样
No, but they had the same rallying point as us.

556
01:04:19,590 --> 01:04:21,490
指出来
Show me.

557
01:04:22,360 --> 01:04:27,850
我们累透了 再待三小时  入夜后出发
My men are beat. We'll hold up here for three hours and pull out after dark.

558
01:04:28,060 --> 01:04:30,760
这镇上有三星级饭店什么的吗
Got anything left in this town, like a three-star hotel?

559
01:04:30,970 --> 01:04:34,070
有干净的床单、枕头 和客房服务吗?
Something with clean sheets, soft pillows and room service?

560
01:04:34,280 --> 01:04:37,670
舒适的教堂如何? 也好
-How about a nice, comfy church? -We'll take that.

561
01:04:37,910 --> 01:04:40,700
有什么消息?战况如何?
What have you heard? How is it all falling together?

562
01:04:40,910 --> 01:04:45,070
我们攻下了滩头堡 但蒙蒂却慢条斯理的进军康城
We got the beachhead secured,but Monty's taking his time moving on Caen.

563
01:04:45,280 --> 01:04:49,310
要他准备好我们才能撤军 大家高估他了
-We can't pull out'til he's ready,so...  -That guy's overrated.

564
01:04:49,520 --> 01:04:53,010
我同意 要拿下康城才能攻取圣罗
-No argument here.  -You take Caen to take Saint-L8.

565
01:04:53,220 --> 01:04:56,820
要攻取瓦隆尼先要拿下圣罗 瓦隆尼之后是瑟堡
-You gotta take St-L8 to take Valognes. -Valognes,you've got Cherbourg.

566
01:04:57,020 --> 01:05:00,460
瑟堡之后是巴黎 最后是柏林
-Cherbourg,you've got Paris.  -Paris,you've got Berlin.

567
01:05:00,690 --> 01:05:03,140
然后就能回家
And then that big boat home.

568
01:05:06,400 --> 01:05:10,100
你在这里能帮到我很多 但我了解你的任务
I could really use you around here, but I understand what you're doing.

569
01:05:10,300 --> 01:05:14,430
是吗? 我也有几个兄弟
-You do?  -I've got a couple of brothers myself.

570
01:05:14,640 --> 01:05:16,770
原来是这样 祝你好运
Oh. Good luck.

571
01:05:16,980 --> 01:05:19,470
谢谢 不  我是说真的
-Thank you.   -No, I mean it.

572
01:05:19,680 --> 01:05:22,740
找他出来  带他回家
Find him. Get him home.

573
01:05:30,590 --> 01:05:32,680
你的手怎么了?
What's with your hand?

574
01:05:33,960 --> 01:05:36,260
不知道
I don't know.

575
01:05:37,500 --> 01:05:40,440
在朴次茅斯上船后就是这样
It started in Portsmouth when we went down for embarkation.

576
01:05:40,640 --> 01:05:45,260
偶尔会这样 你该找别的工作
-It comes and goes.  -You have to find yourself a new job.

577
01:05:45,470 --> 01:05:48,100
这工作不适合你了
This one doesn't seem to agree with you any more.

578
01:05:54,050 --> 01:05:55,710
干嘛?
What?

579
01:06:00,020 --> 01:06:01,950
干嘛? 没什么
-What?   -Nothing.

580
01:06:02,160 --> 01:06:04,890
在安济奥那小子叫什么名字?
What was the name of that kid at Anzio?

581
01:06:05,090 --> 01:06:08,080
用手倒立走路那个
The one who walked on his hands -

582
01:06:08,300 --> 01:06:11,060
唱着空中飞人之歌那个?
and was singing that song about the man on the flying trapeze?

583
01:06:11,270 --> 01:06:14,060
维驰奥 维驰奥
Vecchio. Vecchio!

584
01:06:19,750 --> 01:06:23,440
不错  他是个笨蛋
Yeah, Vecchio. He was a goofy kid.

585
01:06:24,610 --> 01:06:29,910
喜欢在别人的外套上尿出 一个“V”字  代表维驰奥
I remember he used to pee a "v" on everybody's jackets. For "vecchio".

586
01:06:30,120 --> 01:06:33,050
代表胜利 维驰奥
For victory. Vecchio.

587
01:06:35,790 --> 01:06:39,450
他长得很矮 是个侏儒吧?
He was so short. He was a midget, wasn't he?

588
01:06:39,660 --> 01:06:43,460
那他怎么能当上突击队队员?
Yeah, how did he get to be a Ranger?

589
01:06:43,660 --> 01:06:46,260
他的脚给打断了 所以用手走路
He got shot in the foot once, walking on his hands.

590
01:06:46,470 --> 01:06:50,270
走得很快
He could walk faster on his hands.

591
01:06:50,470 --> 01:06:53,340
跑得更加快
He could run faster on his hands.

592
01:06:56,110 --> 01:06:59,770
维驰奥
Vecchio. Yeah.

593
01:07:01,480 --> 01:07:03,750
卡帕佐
Caparzo.

594
01:07:09,320 --> 01:07:15,190
每当一位弟兄死去
You see, when you end up killing one of your men, -

595
01:07:15,400 --> 01:07:20,100
就要告诉自己  这样能拯救
you tell yourself it happened so you could save the lives of -

596
01:07:20,300 --> 01:07:24,530
二、三、四或十条人命
two, three, or ten others.

597
01:07:25,770 --> 01:07:28,210
甚至是一百人
Maybe 100 others.

598
01:07:31,910 --> 01:07:34,810
你知道我当指挥时 有多少部下阵亡吗?
Do you know how many men I've lost under my command?

599
01:07:35,020 --> 01:07:37,280
多少? 94个
-How many?  -94.

600
01:07:38,450 --> 01:07:44,360
但那代表我救了 十倍那么多的人吗?
But that means I've saved the lives of ten times that many, doesn't it?

601
01:07:45,430 --> 01:07:49,420
甚至是二十倍?
Maybe even 20, right? 20 times as many?

602
01:07:54,840 --> 01:07:58,030
事情就是这么简单
And that's how simple it is.

603
01:07:58,240 --> 01:08:03,400
就是这样把任务与属下之间
That's how you rationalise making the choice -

604
01:08:03,610 --> 01:08:06,670
所做的选择合理化
between the mission and the men.

605
01:08:06,880 --> 01:08:09,750
但这次任务正是救人
Except that this time the mission is a man.

606
01:08:13,490 --> 01:08:16,050
这个瑞恩最好值得我们去救
This Ryan had better be worth it.

607
01:08:18,790 --> 01:08:21,490
他回家后最好能行医救人
He'd better go home and cure some disease -

608
01:08:21,700 --> 01:08:25,860
或发明长寿灯泡什么的
or invent a longer-lasting light-bulb or something.

609
01:08:26,070 --> 01:08:30,500
我想十个瑞恩也抵不了 一个卡帕佐或维驰奥
For the truth is that I wouldn't trade ten Ryans for one Vecchio or Caparzo.

610
01:08:30,700 --> 01:08:32,500
阿们
Amen.

611
01:08:34,580 --> 01:08:38,100
你看  又来了 长官
Look, there it goes again. Sir.

612
01:08:39,580 --> 01:08:41,170
还好吧?
Are you alright?

613
01:08:45,690 --> 01:08:50,420
两小时后出发?小睡片刻吧
We'll move out in two hours. Why don't you get some sleep?

614
01:08:51,430 --> 01:08:54,420
不知道他怎么能做到的 什么?
-I don't know how he does it.  -What's that?

615
01:08:54,630 --> 01:08:57,150
如此熟睡  你看
Falls asleep like that. Look at him.

616
01:08:57,360 --> 01:09:00,330
他躺下就睡着了
The guy's lights-out the minute his head hits the pack.

617
01:09:00,530 --> 01:09:03,870
因为问心无愧 有句话怎么说?
-Clear conscience.  -What's that saying?

618
01:09:04,070 --> 01:09:06,370
神与我们同在 那谁与敌军同在?
God's on our side, who could be on theirs?

619
01:09:06,570 --> 01:09:09,540
若神与我们同在 谁会是我们的对手?
"If God be for us, who could be against us?"

620
01:09:09,740 --> 01:09:11,840
不错  我说了什么?
Yeah, what did I say?

621
01:09:12,050 --> 01:09:16,210
想睡着的话  保持清醒就行了
The trick to falling asleep is trying to stay awake.

622
01:09:16,420 --> 01:09:18,080
为什么  韦德?
How is that, Wade?

623
01:09:18,290 --> 01:09:23,190
我妈当实习医师时 习惯在夜间工作
When my mother was an intern she used to work through the night -

624
01:09:23,420 --> 01:09:24,820
白天睡觉
and sleep through the day.

625
01:09:25,830 --> 01:09:29,160
只有她回家  我们才能聊天
The only time we talked was when she'd get home.

626
01:09:29,360 --> 01:09:36,290
我总会躺着  尽量保持清醒 但从没成功过
I used to lie in bed and stay awake as long as I could,but it never worked

627
01:09:36,500 --> 01:09:40,800
越不想睡  就越快睡着
because the harder I tried the faster I'd fall asleep.

628
01:09:41,010 --> 01:09:44,240
但在家里没关系 因为妈会回家
That wouldn't have mattered in my house.Ma would've come home,

629
01:09:44,440 --> 01:09:49,580
把我弄醒  聊至天亮 聊天时她总是不嫌累
shook me awake,chatted me up 'til dawn.She was never too tired to talk.

630
01:09:49,780 --> 01:09:53,050
也许她在那个时候 才有机会讲话
That's probably the only time she could get a word in.

631
01:09:57,820 --> 01:10:01,420
有趣的是 有时她下班时间早了
Funny thing is,sometimes she would come home early

632
01:10:01,630 --> 01:10:03,990
我会假装睡着
and I'd pretend to be asleep.

633
01:10:04,200 --> 01:10:08,030
谁?你妈? 对
-Who, your mum?  -Yeah.

634
01:10:10,570 --> 01:10:13,970
她会站在门口看着我
She'd stand in the doorway looking at me,

635
01:10:14,170 --> 01:10:17,040
我就闭眼装睡
and I would just keep my eyes shut.

636
01:10:19,180 --> 01:10:23,080
我知道她特地早些回来
And I knew that she just wanted to find out about my day,

637
01:10:23,320 --> 01:10:29,780
跟我聊天  了解那天的生活
that she came home early just to talk to me.

638
01:10:32,630 --> 01:10:36,690
但我却仍然不动 假装已经熟睡
And I still wouldn't move. I'd still pretend to be asleep.

639
01:10:43,800 --> 01:10:46,140
我也不知道为何会那样做
I don't know why I did that.

640
01:10:59,690 --> 01:11:03,090
只有几个钟头  闭嘴睡觉吧
We've only got a couple of hours. Shut up and go to sleep.

641
01:11:12,070 --> 01:11:15,330
上尉?长官?
Captain? Sir?

642
01:11:16,940 --> 01:11:18,560
下士
Corporal.

643
01:11:23,180 --> 01:11:26,510
你怎么了?没事吧?
How are you doing? Are you alright?

644
01:11:26,710 --> 01:11:29,840
还好  我想这一切对我有益
Yeah, I think this is all good for me, sir.

645
01:11:31,350 --> 01:11:34,880
真的?为什么?
Really? How is that?

646
01:11:38,960 --> 01:11:43,330
“战争能训练判断力 磨练意志”
'War educates the senses, calls into action the will," -

647
01:11:43,530 --> 01:11:46,690
“增强体格”
"perfects the physical constitution," -

648
01:11:46,900 --> 01:11:50,630
“人在生死关头的瞬间”
"brings men in such swift and close collision in critical moments," -

649
01:11:50,840 --> 01:11:53,170
“强弱立判”
'that man measures man."

650
01:11:53,370 --> 01:11:58,140
爱默森也许是 这样让自己积极起来的
I guess that's Emerson's way of finding the bright side.

651
01:11:58,350 --> 01:12:02,650
你也有读爱默森? 懂一些
-You know Emerson, sir?   -I know some.

652
01:12:06,450 --> 01:12:10,790
上尉  你来自哪里? 在战前你是做什么的?
So, where are you from, Captain? What did you do before the war?

653
01:12:12,560 --> 01:12:14,580
赌金有多少了?
What's the pool up to?

654
01:12:18,370 --> 01:12:21,770
大概是三百块吧
I think it's around 300, sir.

655
01:12:21,970 --> 01:12:26,600
等到了五百的时候 我就把答案告诉你  瓜分赌金
When it gets up to 500,I'll give you the answer and we'll split the money.

656
01:12:26,810 --> 01:12:28,800
如何?
How about that?

657
01:12:29,010 --> 01:12:32,410
要是你这么想 我就有责任建议你
If that's the way you feel, I feel it's my duty under your command

658
01:12:32,610 --> 01:12:37,520
等赌金累积到一千块
to suggest that we wait until it gets up to 1,000. I think it's...

659
01:12:38,720 --> 01:12:41,280
要是活不了那么久呢?
What if we don't live that long?

660
01:12:44,220 --> 01:12:47,280
五百? 五百好
-500?  -500 would be good, yes.

661
01:12:47,490 --> 01:12:49,430
对  长官
Yes, sir.

662
01:12:52,100 --> 01:12:55,190
睡吧  下士 是  长官
-Get some sleep, Corporal.  -Yes, sir.

663
01:14:01,270 --> 01:14:03,460
谁有磺胺粉?
Who's got sulfa powder?

664
01:14:06,070 --> 01:14:10,300
医护兵  我弟兄在流血 需要止血带
Medic, my buddy's bleeding! He needs a tourniquet.

665
01:14:10,510 --> 01:14:11,530
韦德 什么事?
-Wade.   -Yes, sir?

666
01:14:11,750 --> 01:14:13,980
去帮他一下 是
-See what you can do.   -Yes, sir.

667
01:14:14,180 --> 01:14:17,280
撑着  很快就有人来救你
Hold on, fellas. It won't be much longer.

668
01:14:17,480 --> 01:14:19,850
情况如何?
How are we doing here?

669
01:14:20,050 --> 01:14:25,890
没事的  别担心  医师来了
Alright. You're doing alright, don't worry about it. The Doc's in town.

670
01:14:27,490 --> 01:14:31,290
放心  29步兵团已作突围 很快到这里
Don't worry. The 29th Infantry's breaking through. They'll be here soon.

671
01:14:31,500 --> 01:14:33,800
谁有血浆?
Has anybody got plasma?

672
01:14:34,000 --> 01:14:35,930
上尉
Hey, Captain!

673
01:14:36,140 --> 01:14:39,630
有什么事吗? 我是德温得中尉
-Soldier,you want to fill me in?  -Yeah.Lieutenant DeWindt.

674
01:14:39,840 --> 01:14:43,610
隶属于第99运兵中队 负责运载300与307滑翔机步兵
99th Troop Carrier Squadron carrying in 300th and 307th Glider Infantry.

675
01:14:43,810 --> 01:14:46,540
我是飞行员 二等兵
This one was mine. I was the pilot. Private!

676
01:14:46,750 --> 01:14:48,010
22人阵亡 照顾他
22 men dead. Take care of this one.

677
01:14:48,220 --> 01:14:50,980
我着陆时没受伤 副驾驶却死了
I landed there without a scratch, took my co-pilot's head right off.

678
01:14:51,180 --> 01:14:52,910
这些人是谁?
Who are these people?

679
01:14:53,120 --> 01:14:57,320
我们载的士兵第一晚就离开 之后没再见过他们
The guys we came in with headed off the first night. Haven't seen them since.

680
01:14:57,520 --> 01:15:01,430
期间别的士兵 三五成群地陆续出现
In the meantime other guys keep showing up. One, two, six at a time.

681
01:15:01,630 --> 01:15:04,430
然后有军官来把散兵凑成部队
Then some officer will come along, patch together a mixed unit, -

682
01:15:04,630 --> 01:15:06,960
再次出发作战
and head off to make trouble.

683
01:15:07,170 --> 01:15:11,370
我们在找101师 506B连的二等兵瑞恩
We're looking for a Private Ryan, Baker Company, 506th of the 101st.

684
01:15:11,570 --> 01:15:13,730
这可问倒我了  这里人来人往
You got me. A lot of guys come in and out.

685
01:15:13,940 --> 01:15:17,170
厄本  到那队人里面找瑞恩
Upham! Check out that squad. See if Ryan's in it.

686
01:15:17,380 --> 01:15:19,110
是的  长官
Yes, sir.

687
01:15:20,510 --> 01:15:25,650
莱宾  闻闻他的腿 像不像臭乳酪
Reiben! Smell that leg, right there. Find out if it's south of cheese.

688
01:15:32,160 --> 01:15:34,180
如何?
What?

689
01:15:34,390 --> 01:15:36,790
手放头上
Hands over your head.

690
01:15:38,670 --> 01:15:40,530
别停下来!
Keep moving!

691
01:15:43,370 --> 01:15:45,130
我是犹太人
I'm Jude, you know.

692
01:15:47,810 --> 01:15:51,570
无法把他弄出来  要有绞车
I couldn't pry him out of there. I need a winch.

693
01:15:51,780 --> 01:15:53,370
是的
Yeah.

694
01:15:56,620 --> 01:15:58,850
星级上将 对
-Stars.  -Yeah.

695
01:15:59,050 --> 01:16:03,460
阿门准将 101空降师的副指挥官
Brigadier General Amend. Deputy Commander, 101st.

696
01:16:03,690 --> 01:16:08,420
有些天才提议 在机舱焊接钢板
Some genius had the great idea of welding steel plates onto our deck

697
01:16:08,630 --> 01:16:10,990
以免地面的炮火伤及上将
to keep the General safe from ground fire,

698
01:16:11,200 --> 01:16:15,330
但他们到空降前才告诉我们
but they forgot to tell me until just before we were getting airborne.

699
01:16:15,540 --> 01:16:19,060
就像开货运列车飞行般?
That's like trying to fly a freight train. OK?

700
01:16:19,270 --> 01:16:22,900
负荷过重  地面炮火又猛烈
Gross overload. Trim characteristics all shot to hell.

701
01:16:23,110 --> 01:16:25,980
我为了保持平衡 手几乎都弄断了
I nearly broke both my arms trying to keep her level.

702
01:16:26,180 --> 01:16:30,480
脱勾时我已经尽力了
When we released I cut as hard as I could,

703
01:16:30,680 --> 01:16:33,980
尝试保持高度  以免失速
trying to gain some altitude and keep her from stalling.

704
01:16:34,190 --> 01:16:39,060
最后像陨石一样掉下来 结果变成这样
We came down like a fucking meteor. And this is how we ended up.

705
01:16:40,630 --> 01:16:43,890
其他飞机总算顺利着陆
The others stopped easy enough, though.

706
01:16:44,100 --> 01:16:47,660
我们的飞机太重了
We were just too damn heavy, you know?

707
01:16:47,870 --> 01:16:53,100
草地湿滑  而且是下坡
The grass was wet. Downward slope and all.

708
01:16:53,310 --> 01:16:55,600
死了22人
22 guys dead.

709
01:16:57,940 --> 01:17:01,850
全为了一个上将? 一个人
-All that for a general?  -One man.

710
01:17:03,720 --> 01:17:06,850
这种事很多 “苦差”
There's a lot of that going around. "FUBAR."

711
01:17:07,720 --> 01:17:09,710
“苦差” “苦差”
-"FUBAR."  -"FUBAR."

712
01:17:10,420 --> 01:17:14,450
“苦差” 都说对了
"FUBAR."  -You all got that right.

713
01:17:14,660 --> 01:17:17,360
我在德语字典中 查不到“苦差”
I looked it up in a German dictionary. "FUBAR"'s not there.

714
01:17:17,560 --> 01:17:20,090
厄本  那边也有伞兵
Upham! There are more paratroopers out there.

715
01:17:20,300 --> 01:17:22,630
去找瑞恩
Find out if one of them is Ryan.

716
01:17:22,840 --> 01:17:25,770
你可在这里找找
You might want to check this out, sir.

717
01:17:25,970 --> 01:17:29,460
是兵籍牌  多得数不完
Dog tags. More than I really want to count, sir.

718
01:17:31,440 --> 01:17:34,380
我已盖过许多尸体
I've covered a lot of bodies, sir.

719
01:17:34,610 --> 01:17:39,310
杰克森  从这些开始找吧 是
-Jackson. Start going through those.  -Yes, sir.

720
01:17:40,390 --> 01:17:41,550
我来帮忙
I'll help.

721
01:17:44,560 --> 01:17:49,050
你觉得有那小子吗? 有的话  我会找到的
-Do you think that little prick's in there?  -If he is,I'm going to find him.

722
01:17:49,260 --> 01:17:51,990
我敢说那混蛋... 我打赌他还活着
I bet that son of a bitch... I've got money saying he's still alive.

723
01:17:52,200 --> 01:17:56,000
赌十块我会先找到 来看这里有什么
0 bucks says I nail him first. Let's see what we've got in here.

724
01:17:56,200 --> 01:17:59,070
你没希望了 你认为他在这里面吗?
You mugs don't stand a chance. Do you think he's in here?

725
01:17:59,270 --> 01:18:01,900
继续找吧 好吧
Just keep looking. Alright.

726
01:18:02,110 --> 01:18:07,310
盖瑞艾尼高、班瑞比诺 麦克塞里奥  全都是几内亚人
"Gary lanico", "Ben Rubino", "Mike Cesario"...All the Guineas are buying it.

727
01:18:07,510 --> 01:18:11,920
不是这名字 维维里维基  是你的朋友
Come on, it's not the right name! 'Wee Willie Winkie". A buddy of yours.

728
01:18:12,720 --> 01:18:14,650
我们得找到那混蛋
We've got to find this prick.

729
01:18:19,160 --> 01:18:20,920
那混蛋在哪里?
Where's this son of a bitch?

730
01:18:21,130 --> 01:18:23,430
别混在一起  分开一点
Don't mix them up. Keep them in your pile.

731
01:18:23,630 --> 01:18:25,930
怎么知道哪些是看过的呢?
How am I supposed to know who we've got?

732
01:18:26,130 --> 01:18:28,760
莱宾  闭嘴好吗?
Why don't you just shut up, Reiben?

733
01:18:28,970 --> 01:18:33,200
别吵架 你不高兴吗?
Everybody be friends. Cranky there, huh?

734
01:18:33,410 --> 01:18:36,270
有优胜者了 你说什么?
-I think I've got a winner.  -What are you talking about?

735
01:18:36,480 --> 01:18:38,710
瑞恩 瑞恩?
"Ryan." Ryan?

736
01:18:38,910 --> 01:18:42,440
梅利西  你看 你简直是天才
Take a look at that, Mellis. You're really a genius.

737
01:18:42,650 --> 01:18:47,180
这是里恩  是法语名字 知道这是什么意思吗?
"R-l-E-N-N-E." That's "Rienne" and it's French. Do you know what that means?

738
01:18:47,390 --> 01:18:49,980
一无所获 什么比三条大?
It means "nothing". What beats three of a kind?

739
01:18:50,190 --> 01:18:54,560
这些人全都来自纽约 你老是发牢骚
I got shit here, all guys from New York. You're always bitching.

740
01:18:54,760 --> 01:18:56,700
要帮忙吗? 我葫芦
Do you need a hand? I've got a full house.

741
01:18:56,900 --> 01:18:59,890
我赢了  同花顺
I've got you beat. Straight flush.

742
01:19:00,100 --> 01:19:03,370
你偷看我的牌  你作弊
You're looking at my cards. You're cheating.

743
01:19:03,570 --> 01:19:07,510
笨得太离谱了  你识字吗?
Fucking unreal, this guy. Can you read that shit?

744
01:19:07,740 --> 01:19:12,300
老天  你看这可怜的砘 大概不能防弹吧
Jesus, look at this poor bastard! I guess they're not bulletproof.

745
01:19:12,510 --> 01:19:13,740
应该不能
I guess not.

746
01:19:13,950 --> 01:19:18,480
这砘锩荒源 跟你的那里一样
I don't like what's between his ears.It's like what's between your legs.

747
01:19:18,690 --> 01:19:22,090
对极了 杰克森  说得没错
We've got to give him that. That's not bad for you, Jackson.

748
01:19:22,320 --> 01:19:25,160
我三条 你在干嘛?
I've got three of a kind. What the hell are you doing?

749
01:19:25,360 --> 01:19:29,120
整个空降师都在看着 这可不是扑克牌
The whole goddam Airborne's watching. These aren't poker chips.

750
01:19:29,330 --> 01:19:31,800
好吧 放回去
Alright. Put them back in there.

751
01:19:56,560 --> 01:19:58,180
他不在这里
He's not here.

752
01:20:02,730 --> 01:20:05,160
也许我们该分头去找吧?
Maybe we should split into groups?

753
01:20:05,400 --> 01:20:07,590
到树林里去叫他的名字
Just wander the woods calling his name.

754
01:20:07,800 --> 01:20:10,530
他迟早会听到的  瑞恩
He's bound to hear us sooner or later. Ryan!

755
01:20:10,740 --> 01:20:14,300
上尉  这也不是办法
That might be a little hard to do, Captain.

756
01:20:14,510 --> 01:20:21,280
也许本地人见过他 瑞恩  詹姆斯瑞恩?
Maybe the locals have seen him. Ryan, James Ryan?

757
01:20:21,480 --> 01:20:25,140
瑞恩?有人认识 101空降师的瑞恩吗?
Ryan! Anybody know Ryan, 101st Airborne? You know Ryan?

758
01:20:25,350 --> 01:20:30,250
爱阿华州的二等兵瑞恩?
Private James Ryan from lowa? Anybody know a Ryan?

759
01:20:30,460 --> 01:20:33,890
瑞恩 阿乔
James Ryan! Hey, Joe!

760
01:20:34,130 --> 01:20:38,360
麦可森不是认识C连的瑞恩吗
Doesn't Michaelson pal around with a Ryan from C Company?

761
01:20:38,570 --> 01:20:41,830
应该是 带他过来
I think so. Bring him up.

762
01:20:51,210 --> 01:20:53,440
你认识二等兵瑞恩? 你要大声一点
-You know Private Ryan?  -You have to speak up...

763
01:20:53,650 --> 01:20:56,840
大声一点  我的耳朵不灵光
You have to speak up, sir! My hearing is not so good!

764
01:20:57,050 --> 01:20:59,880
手榴弹在耳朵边爆炸 听力时有时无的
It comes and goes. A grenade went off right by my head.

765
01:21:00,090 --> 01:21:04,580
你认识二等兵瑞恩? 谁?
-Got it. Do you know Private Ryan?   -Who?

766
01:21:04,890 --> 01:21:08,380
二等兵瑞恩?詹姆斯瑞恩? 吉米瑞恩?
-Private Ryan? James Ryan?  -Jimmy Ryan?

767
01:21:08,590 --> 01:21:11,430
詹姆斯法兰西斯瑞恩
James. James Francis Ryan.

768
01:21:11,630 --> 01:21:14,600
不  是詹姆斯法兰西斯瑞恩
No, no, no. James Francis Ryan.

769
01:21:14,830 --> 01:21:17,890
给我纸笔
Give me a pencil. Something to write on.

770
01:21:18,100 --> 01:21:19,590
快点  铅笔
Quick, a pencil!

771
01:21:21,910 --> 01:21:23,740
小铅笔给你
Here you are, a small one.

772
01:21:24,780 --> 01:21:29,610
写下来  詹姆斯法兰西斯瑞恩 爱阿华州?
Write this down: "James Francis Ryan? Iowa?"

773
01:21:29,820 --> 01:21:33,620
你认识他吗?你自己看
"Do you know him?" Read the message! Look!

774
01:21:36,290 --> 01:21:40,060
我当然认识他 知道他在哪里吗?
-Yeah, of course I know him.  -Does he know where he is?

775
01:21:44,130 --> 01:21:47,400
我们偏离了降落区二十英里
Yeah, we missed our dropzone by about 20 miles

776
01:21:47,600 --> 01:21:50,800
降落的地方好像是 布鲁维里什么的
and ended up way over by "Bumville" or some damn place.

777
01:21:51,000 --> 01:21:54,060
我跟他和其他人 正要到了这里集合
Him, me and a couple of others were coming here to the rally point.

778
01:21:54,270 --> 01:21:59,910
却遇到一位上校 正召集弟兄前往兰姆勒
We ran into a colonel who was gathering up men to go to Ramelle.

779
01:22:00,110 --> 01:22:02,170
兰姆勒? 去防守一座桥
Ramelle? To babysit a bridge.

780
01:22:02,380 --> 01:22:05,320
那是我最后一次看见他 好极了  谢谢
-That's the last I've seen of him.  -Great! Thank you!

781
01:22:05,550 --> 01:22:08,610
写谢谢  你看  谢谢 不客气
-Write "Thank you". Read. Thank you.  -You're welcome!

782
01:22:08,820 --> 01:22:10,550
大家过来
Assemble on me.

783
01:22:12,560 --> 01:22:14,490
谢谢你  中尉
Thank you, Lieutenant.

784
01:22:17,160 --> 01:22:19,130
兰姆勒
Ramelle.

785
01:22:20,130 --> 01:22:25,570
我们在这里 兰姆勒在麦德里特河畔
We're here. There. Ramelle is on the Merderet River,right here.

786
01:22:25,810 --> 01:22:27,860
在我们的西南方
Just to the southwest of us.

787
01:22:28,070 --> 01:22:30,370
你知道那座桥吗?
You know anything about that bridge we just talk about?

788
01:22:30,580 --> 01:22:34,980
知道  瑟堡一直是盟军的目标
Yeah. The target has always been Cherbourg.

789
01:22:35,180 --> 01:22:40,310
要占领深水港  才能攻占巴黎 而隆美尔也知道
We can't push on Paris until we take a deep water port and Rommel knows that.

790
01:22:40,520 --> 01:22:45,010
他会试着把装甲部队 运过麦德里特河
He's going to try to get his armour across the Merderet River anyway he can.

791
01:22:45,220 --> 01:22:50,060
这样就能在我们 进攻瑟堡时夹击我们
That way he can hit us in the flank when we make the turn for Cherbourg.

792
01:22:50,260 --> 01:22:56,000
所以有桥梁的村庄 都成了重要的据点
That makes any village on the river with a bridge solid gold real estate.

793
01:23:16,320 --> 01:23:17,650
走吧
Let's go.

794
01:23:27,230 --> 01:23:28,790
上尉
Captain.

795
01:24:07,010 --> 01:24:09,870
那是什么?
What the hell is that?

796
01:24:10,080 --> 01:24:13,050
废弃的雷达站
A radar site. It's got to be out of action.

797
01:24:13,280 --> 01:24:19,180
下面的沙坑里有敌人
Looks like we've got something in that sandbag bunker under the station.

798
01:24:19,420 --> 01:24:23,380
看到吗? 对  我也这么想
-See it?   -Yeah, that's my guess, too.

799
01:24:23,620 --> 01:24:28,490
那是什么? 机枪  或许是MG-42
-What is it?    -Machine gun, probably MG-42.

800
01:24:28,690 --> 01:24:32,560
那些人就是被它干掉的? 也许瑞恩也在里面
-Is that what got those guys?  -Maybe one of them is Ryan.

801
01:24:32,770 --> 01:24:35,700
不  他们是82队的 你的运气才没那么好
No, their patches are 82nd, so your luck's not that good.

802
01:24:35,940 --> 01:24:40,670
我不知道你们的脚程 但若我们悄悄地绕道
I don't know how fast you are, but if we detour this way quick and quiet,

803
01:24:40,870 --> 01:24:42,570
德军就不会知道我们在这里
the Krauts will never even know we were here.

804
01:24:44,210 --> 01:24:47,580
为何不绕道走?
What I'm trying to say is why don't we just go around the thing?

805
01:24:47,780 --> 01:24:51,510
我明白  但不能够这样
I hear what you're saying, but we can't go around it.

806
01:24:52,990 --> 01:24:56,610
我支持莱宾的说法 避开那些机枪就行了
I'm with Reiben. I mean, we left those 88s.

807
01:24:57,520 --> 01:25:03,330
空军可不会专程来 对付一挺机枪
For the Air Force. They're not going to spend ordnance on one machine gun.

808
01:25:03,530 --> 01:25:04,790
上尉
Captain.

809
01:25:06,070 --> 01:25:10,930
绕路还是能达成任务 这并不是我们的任务  对吧?
We can skip it and still accomplish our mission. This isn't our mission, right?

810
01:25:11,140 --> 01:25:13,330
梅利西  你想这样做吗?
Is that what you want to do, Mellish?

811
01:25:13,540 --> 01:25:16,010
任由其他部队中伏?
Leave it here so they can ambush another company?

812
01:25:16,240 --> 01:25:21,940
不  我只是说 这并非我们的目标
No, I'm simply saying it's seems an unnecessary risk given our objective.

813
01:25:22,150 --> 01:25:24,580
