02:31:55,310 --> 02:31:57,070
麦克
Mike!

1316
02:32:01,850 --> 02:32:03,610
麦克
Mike!

1317
02:32:46,090 --> 02:32:50,150
上尉  你去哪里?回来
Captain, where the hell are you going? Captain, get back here!

1318
02:34:43,280 --> 02:34:44,710
厄本
Upham!

1319
02:35:14,370 --> 02:35:16,500
撑着
Hang in there.

1320
02:36:01,890 --> 02:36:03,860
救护员
Medic!

1321
02:36:06,460 --> 02:36:09,120
有救护员吗?
Medic! We've got a medic?

1322
02:36:15,770 --> 02:36:19,460
是P-51反坦克轰炸机
They're tankbusters, sir. P-51s.

1323
02:36:19,670 --> 02:36:21,760
我们的守护天使
Angels on our shoulders.

1324
02:36:27,780 --> 02:36:29,870
什么事?
What, sir?

1325
02:36:33,920 --> 02:36:35,980
詹姆斯
James...

1326
02:36:37,220 --> 02:36:39,350
别辜负
Earn this.

1327
02:36:42,930 --> 02:36:45,290
别辜负大家
Earn it.

1328
02:37:13,630 --> 02:37:16,890
“亲爱的瑞恩太太”
"My dear Mrs Ryan."

1329
02:37:17,100 --> 02:37:21,030
“我有个喜讯要带给你”
"It's with a profound sense of joy that I write to inform you"

1330
02:37:21,270 --> 02:37:25,570
“就是令O二等兵 詹姆斯瑞恩安然无恙”
"that your son, Private James Ryan, is well"-

1331
02:37:25,770 --> 02:37:30,540
“现在正从欧洲的战线回国”
"and at this moment on his way home from European battlefields."

1332
02:37:30,740 --> 02:37:34,910
“詹姆斯尽忠职守”
"Reports indicate that James did his duty in combat"

1333
02:37:35,110 --> 02:37:38,140
“勇气过人  坚毅不屈”
"with great courage and steadfast dedication"

1334
02:37:38,380 --> 02:37:42,880
“纵使他得悉兄弟阵亡”
"even after he was informed of the loss your family has suffered"

1335
02:37:43,120 --> 02:37:48,060
“仍坚持参与这场 铲除独裁暴政的伟大抗争”
"in this great campaign to rid the world of tyranny and oppression."

1336
02:37:48,290 --> 02:37:51,230
“我与战争部长”
"I take great pleasure injoining the Secretary of War, "

1337
02:37:51,460 --> 02:37:56,400
“美军同仁及美国国民”
"the men and women of the US Army, and the citizens of a grateful nation"

1338
02:37:56,640 --> 02:38:02,670
“仅此祝你身体健康 与詹姆斯一起活得愉快”
"in wishing you good health and many years of happiness with James."

1339
02:38:02,910 --> 02:38:07,370
“虽然爱子平安归国”
"Nothing, not even the safe return of a beloved son"

1340
02:38:07,610 --> 02:38:11,610
“也无法弥补你 和千千万万个美国家庭”
"can compensate you or the thousands of other American families"

1341
02:38:11,850 --> 02:38:15,150
“在战争中遭受的创痛”
"who have suffered great loss in this tragic war."

1342
02:38:15,350 --> 02:38:17,250
“我想与你分享”
"I might share with you some words"-

1343
02:38:17,460 --> 02:38:22,920
“一番在悲痛绝望中 支持着我的说话”
"which have sustained me through nights of peril, loss and heartache, "

1344
02:38:23,160 --> 02:38:27,150
“是这样的一番说话”
"and I quote, 'I pray that our heavenly Father"

1345
02:38:27,400 --> 02:38:30,700
“愿天主安抚你的丧子之痛”
"may assuage the anguish of your bereavement"

1346
02:38:30,900 --> 02:38:34,740
“让你永远怀念远去的挚爱”
"and leave you only the cherished memory of the loved and lost"

1347
02:38:34,940 --> 02:38:37,310
“神圣的荣耀都归于你们”
"and the solemn pride that must be yours"

1348
02:38:37,510 --> 02:38:42,780
“因你们为自由 付出了重大的代价”
"to have laid a so costly a sacrifice upon the altar of freedom."

1349
02:38:42,980 --> 02:38:44,950
“林肯敬上”
"Abraham Lincoln."

1350
02:38:45,180 --> 02:38:47,650
“深表敬意”
"Yours very sincerely and respectfully,"

1351
02:38:47,890 --> 02:38:51,220
“参谋长马歇尔上将”
"George C. Marshall. General, Chief of Staff."

1352
02:39:42,310 --> 02:39:47,300
今天我家人也来了 他们想跟我来
My family is with me today. They wanted to come with me.

1353
02:39:50,380 --> 02:39:55,720
说真的  我不知道到这里来 会有什么感受
To be honest with you, I wasn't sure how I would feel coming back here.

1354
02:39:58,020 --> 02:40:03,760
我每天都想着 当日你在桥上说的话
Every day, I think about what you said to me that day on the bridge.

1355
02:40:05,600 --> 02:40:09,930
我尽力活好我的人生
I've tried to live my life the best I could.

1356
02:40:10,140 --> 02:40:13,160
希望这已经足够
I hope that was enough.

1357
02:40:13,410 --> 02:40:17,740
希望这至少让你觉得...
I hope that at least in your eyes...

1358
02:40:17,940 --> 02:40:21,880
我没有辜负 你们为我做的一切
l've earned what all of you have done for me.

1359
02:40:35,190 --> 02:40:37,220
詹姆斯
James.

1360
02:40:38,760 --> 02:40:41,790
“约翰米勒上尉”
"Captain John H. Miller."

1361
02:40:49,470 --> 02:40:54,410
跟我说我这辈子没白活 什么?
-Tell me I have led a good life. -What?

1362
02:40:54,650 --> 02:40:57,010
跟我说  我是好人
Tell me I'm a good mess.

1363
02:41:04,120 --> 02:41:06,180
你是好人
You are.

1364
02:42:02,000 --> 02:42:06,000
（米勒上尉，宾州第二突击队　卒于1944年6月13日）

1365
02:42:06,000 --> 02:42:11,000

